  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, on the VWP dataset, the (+LLAMA 2) model achieves the overall lowest d HM, performing better than the LLaVA model.",
    "These results quantitatively indicate that the stories generated by the models are close to the corresponding human-written stories.",
    "To better understand if the metrics are capable of effectively comparing stories generated by models with human-written ones, we conduct a qualitative evaluation, that we describe in the next section.",
    "We observe that as the models increase in size, the scores for the stories they generated get closer to scores of human annotations.",
    "Our results suggest that the stories generated by the best-performing models according to d HM are very close to human levels of visual grounding, coherence, and degree of repetition."
